<div class="com-share" data-id="22002" data-title="《微软公布了应用商店的数据，不好看》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22002/medium/22002.jpg?1454643695" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22002.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
